            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Strange, I can see them on at least two devices (one even without logging in). Maybe they are too big, I'll add some smaller ones as soon as I get back to a computer.\n\nTo describe the images with `vim.o.number` as an example: `vim` is highlighted as `@variable` while `o.number` is highlighted as `@variable.member`, with the default colorscheme these look different, as one is (more or less) linked to `Normal` while the other is linked to `Identifier`. `colors/vim.lua` links both to `Identifier` so they have the same color.",
